  <name>OpenRA - Red Alert Classic</name>
  <summary>An open-source remake of the original Red Alert Classic game</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      OpenRA Red Alert Classic is a project that meticulously recreates the original Command &amp; Conquer: Red Alert real time strategy game, using the open-source OpenRA game engine. 
    </p>
    <p>
      OpenRA Red Alert Classic is free in itself, but it requires assets from the original Command &amp; Conquer: Red Alert game. There are demo assets available for free online, but a more complete and true game experience requires non-free assets from the original game.
    </p>
  </description>
